===Inventory===
A form of sustain, such as full guthans, or a saradomin godsword with lightbearer should be brought over food, as it is very easy to heal due to the bosses' incredibly low defence. 

If no sustains are used, super restores are recommended over prayer potions to make use of saradomin brews, though these are not dropped alongside combat potions and will require the player to boost it back up if the brews are drunk.
